### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts

###

### Get one contact
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/6a5196444b6ef9abca617bfa

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json 

{
  "email": "test1@example.com",
  "username": "test1",
  "name": "Tests",
  "ipaddress": "10.0.10.15",
  "lastName": "Testerson",
  "favoriteColor": "blue",
  "birthday": "1990-01-01"
}

### Update a contact
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/6a5196444b6ef9abca617bfa HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "karla.perez@example.com",
  "username": "Kperez",
  "name": "Karla Perez",
  "ipaddress": "10.0.0.16",
  "lastName": "Perez",
  "favoriteColor": "Red",
  "birthday": "1998-01-01"
}

### Delete a contact
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/6a5196444b6ef9abca617bfa